text:

text:

Kitni bakchodi ki hai apan teeno ne CCD mei beth ke .. Anurag se jang ki kitni tyaari bhi ki thi lol

Kaafi proud hota hai ki saath mei club ko kaafi aachi stage tak pahuncha dia.. Treat to pending reh gayi.. Chill hai jab milenge tab bethenge aur daaru peeyenge..
SOS forever <3

text: Naman Eco trip plan karte hai .. kyuki bonding hogi, Naman P Club project karte hai.. gyaan milega...  Naman yaar room lele, Naman yaar DS karle, Naman SOS karte hai, Naman E-Cell, Techkriti, ..... PC finance..  Never an ending list.. kyuki starting se tumhare saath ideas execute karne mei maje aaye. Yeh sab to wo tha jo plan kia aur kar dia aur bahut kuch reh bhi gaya.. You were the smartest and least appreciated, & best roommate/friend/brother I could get.. Cheers to 4 years of bakchodi/fun and fights we had! <3

text:

text:
Rishabh, aur batao kya chal raha? xD 
From many pointless discussion, I got to know he is one of the most charming people, who can literally make you talk for hours without feeling it bore and definitely not one-sided. I knew him from 1st year when we use to play badminton and discussed how we can plan a cheap trip.  Till then we have sat together in CCD, library, in my room and thought about different philosophy of life. He literally has the power to make you smile with confidence.  Hope to meet you soon.
author: Jay  Gupta

text:
Yo!
I guess, I learned the use of this word from you xD. It will be safe to call you my closest friend in the Eco department. I started knowing you from the E-cell senior exec. and now you are the person with whom I did my maximum courses. You were my chai partner, and definitely, I am going to miss all the fun discussion roaming around the library and drinking tea.  This time we were unfortunate that we didn't get to meet apart from one time which is VH2 quarantine (scariest place to meet anyone xD) but definitely we will go on a compensation trip with eco buddies. Hope to see you soon. :)
author: Jay  Gupta

text:
Sabbu Joginder ji,  kya haal chal?
Tumhara toast reh gaya tha wing ka so, this will be the right place to write about you! 
Firstly, tum na hote to I guess mei OE mei ek baar to F le hi aata xD. Most eco students still don't know the actual reason for my passion for electrical courses (lol). People call you introvert but honestly I didn't felt that because you are my uncalled safe space which neither bothered or nor wanted to sort things. I still don't know why the hell I always scream at you, rant, sometimes fight (Yes I will take revenge of that slap) with you but still laugh and smile after talking to you without thinking about anything else. Honestly, from all those memicary, bitching i can say you are the most funniest person to be hangout with for me. And haa beware of my dreams, sach ho jaate aur tum pe bhaari padh jaate hai xD.
author: Jay  Gupta

text: Bro, u are not innocent xD... yaar saath daaru peene ka plan reh gaya. Chill hai next trip mei compensate kar lenge. I guess u were most funny character in our group, thus only place jaha mere see jyada kisi aur ke maje lia gaye xD... Thanks for that.. Kitne assignment, classes, library mei padhai ki hai tumahre saath ki kya bataye bas itna yaad hai ki bahut maje aate the tumhare saath faltu time pass karne me.. going to miss this whole eco group.. <3
